--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
DESCRIPTION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This role manages net_tools.

The net-tools package contains basic networking tools, including ifconfig,
netstat, route, and others. Most of them are obsolete. For replacement check
iproute package.

For more detailed information on the usage and available configuration options
please consult the following sections.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
USAGE
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

INSTALL
  - hosts: all
    roles:
     - role: net_tools
       net_tools_state: 'install'

REMOVE
  - hosts: all
    roles:
     - role: net_tools
       net_tools_state: 'remove'

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VARIABLES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ROLE
  net_tools_state
    Description: Control the state of the role.
                 'net-tools' is a core package on Gentoo based systems and can
                 therefore not be removed.
    Implemented: 0.1
    Required   : False
    Value      : Predetermined
    Type       : String
    Default    : 'install'
    Options    :
      Install: 'true' | 'yes' | 'install'
      Remove : 'false' | 'no' | 'remove'

